Class PrePopulateBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.tool.bean.PrePopulateBean

  • public class PrePopulateBean
extends Object
    PrePopulateBean is a helper bean which given the currentPageRealm, the currentUser, and a populateService will populate the current page realm.
